<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Sphecodes combai Nobile & Turrisi, 2004, holotype, male A head, frontal view B vertex, dorsal view C metasoma, dorsal view D T 1, dorsal view E genitalia, dorsal view F labels. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 4. Sphecodes walteri Nobile & Turrisi, 2004, holotype, male A head, frontal view B vertex, dorsal view C metasoma, dorsal view D T 1, dorsal view E genitalia, dorsal view F labels. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 3. Sphecodes marcellinoi Nobile & Turrisi, 2004, holotype, male A head, frontal view B vertex, dorsal view C metasoma, dorsal view D T 1, dorsal view E genitalia, dorsal view F labels. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 2. Sphecodes banaszaki Nobile & Turrisi, 2004, holotype, male A head, frontal view B vertex, dorsal view C metasoma, dorsal view D T 1, dorsal view E genitalia, dorsal view F labels. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 5. Sphecodes iosephi Nobile & Turrisi, 2004, holotype, male A head, frontal view B vertex, dorsal view C metasoma, dorsal view D T 1, dorsal view E genitalia, dorsal view F labels. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 6. Sphecodes tomarchioi Nobile & Turrisi, 2004, holotype, male A head, frontal view B vertex, dorsal view C metasoma, dorsal view D T 1, dorsal view E genitalia, dorsal view F labels. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 7. Sphecodes pinguiculus Perez, 1903 (A), S. marginatus Hagens, 1882 (B, D), and S. nomioidis Pesenko, 1979 (C, E), males A head, frontal view B, C antennae, lateral view D, E genitalia, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537876" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537877" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537874" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537875" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537872" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537878" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537873" .

